## PTMs

```python
import pandas as pd
import os
from functools import partial

keepers = ['gene_name', 'recommended_name', 'uniprot', 'ENSG', 'ENST', 'ENSP']
data = pd.DataFrame([], columns=keepers+['residue_idx', 'aa_to_interface'])
for file in os.listdir(f'{ProteinCore.settings.pickle_folder}/taxid9606'):
    if file[-2:] != '.p':
        continue
    p = ProteinCore(uniprot =file[:-2], taxid=9606).load()
    if 'PSP_modified_residues' not in p.features:
        continue
    for feat in p.features['PSP_modified_residues']:
        data = data.append({**{key: getattr(p, key) for key in keepers},
                            **{'residue_idx': feat['residue_index'],
                               'residue_name': feat['from_residue'],
                               'ptm': feat['ptm']}
                           }, ignore_index=True)
# adding pLI
# Variant ID	Gene	Verdict
pLI = pd.read_csv('gnomad.v2.1.1.lof_metrics.by_gene.txt', sep='\t')
ENST2pLI = dict(zip(pLI.transcript.values, pLI.pLI.values))
ENST2pRec = dict(zip(pLI.transcript.values, pLI.pRec.values))
ENST2pNull = dict(zip(pLI.transcript.values, pLI.pNull.values))
def get_from_map(ENST, mapping): return mapping[ENST] if ENST in mapping else float('nan')
get_pLI = partial(get_from_map, mapping=ENST2pLI)
get_pRec = partial(get_from_map, mapping=ENST2pRec)
get_pNull = partial(get_from_map, mapping=ENST2pNull)
data['pLI'] = data.ENST.apply(get_pLI)
data['pRec'] = data.ENST.apply(get_pRec)
data['pNull'] = data.ENST.apply(get_pNull)
data = data.sort_values('pLI', ascending=False)
data.to_csv('ptms.csv')

data['mutation'] = data.apply(lambda row: f'{row.residue_name}{row.residue_idx}X', 1)
mini = data.loc[data.gene_name.apply(len) != 0]
mini['interesting'] = mini.apply(lambda row: f'{row.ENST}|{row.ptm}|{row.pLI}|{row.pRec}', 1)
mini[['gene_name','mutation', 'interesting']].to_csv('ptm4backloc.csv', sep='\t', index=False, header=False)
```
After backlocate:

```python
backed = pd.read_csv('pmt-backlocated.txt', sep='\t')
backed = backed.sort_values(['chromosome','index0.in.genomic'])\
               .drop_duplicates(['chromosome','index0.in.genomic'])
fbacked = backed.loc[backed['extra.user.data'].apply(lambda v: v.split('|')[0]  if isinstance(v, str) else 'ZZZ') == \
                     backed['transcript.id'].apply(lambda v: v.split('.')[0] if isinstance(v, str) else 'XXX')]
fbacked['genomic'] = fbacked['index0.in.genomic'].astype(int)
fbacked['petide'] = fbacked['petide.pos.1'].astype(int)
dfbacked = fbacked.loc[fbacked['extra.user.data'].apply(lambda v: float(v.split('|')[2]) > 0.5 or float(v.split('|')[3]) > 0.5)]
dfbacked = dfbacked.sort_values(['chromosome','genomic'])
sdfbacked = {ptm: dfbacked.loc[dfbacked['extra.user.data'].apply(lambda v: v.split('|')[1] == ptm)] for ptm in ['p', 'm1', 'ub', 'm2', 'sm', 'gl', 'ga', 'm3', 'me']}
print({ptm: len(sdfbacked[ptm]) for ptm in sdfbacked})

# phosphorylation
b = sdfbacked['p'][['transcript.name', 'petide', 'chromosome','genomic']]
b.to_csv('phosphorylation-genomic.csv')
with open('temp.txt', 'w') as fh:
    for i in list(range(1,24))+['X','Y']:
        fh.write(f'\n\nChromosome {i}\n\n')
        fh.write('\t'+';'.join(b.loc[backed.chromosome == f'chr{i}'].genomic.astype(str)))

# methylation
b = pd.concat([sdfbacked['me'][['transcript.name', 'petide', 'chromosome','genomic']],
               sdfbacked['m1'][['transcript.name', 'petide', 'chromosome','genomic']],
               sdfbacked['m2'][['transcript.name', 'petide', 'chromosome','genomic']],
               sdfbacked['m3'][['transcript.name', 'petide', 'chromosome','genomic']],
              ]).sort_values(['chromosome','genomic'])
b.to_csv('methylation-genomic.csv')
with open('temp.txt', 'w') as fh:
    for i in list(range(1,24))+['X','Y']:
        fh.write(f'\n\nChromosome {i}\n\n')
        fh.write('\t'+';'.join(b.loc[backed.chromosome == f'chr{i}'].genomic.astype(str)))
```
